My computer is kinda half dead, so I can't post as often :(

Key looks over to the note left in her quarters. She picks it up with her 
gentle hands and reads it. Then she folds it up and puts in in a drawer. She 
smiles as she hears Liono over the intercom. He really needed to learn to 
controll himself.

Key walks off toward the lab, humming to herself.
